      "start_time": 389.6,
      "end_time": 392.44,
      "language": "en",
      "confidence": -0.09750872566586449
    },
    {
      "text": "So that becomes my second model.",
      "start_time": 393.08,
      "end_time": 395.18,
      "language": "en",
      "confidence": -0.09750872566586449
    },
    {
      "text": "And my third model is like, okay, I understand the language,",
      "start_time": 395.68,
      "end_time": 399.08,
      "language": "en",
      "confidence": -0.09750872566586449
    },
    {
      "text": "I understand your voice.",
      "start_time": 399.12,
      "end_time": 400.18,
      "language": "en",
      "confidence": -0.09750872566586449
    },
    {
      "text": "Now I exactly want to transcribe what you are saying",
